Open Payments API Endpoint (Temporal)

Source: R/S7_backend.R
TemporalOpen.Rd

Open Payments API Endpoint (Temporal)

Usage

TemporalOpen(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <TemporalOpen> object.

Examples
